.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-HTLC-MAX-SET" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-htlc-max-set \- set maximum HTLC size for a channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-htlc-max-set
.I channel_id max_msat
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sets the maximum HTLC size in millisatoshis for the specified channel via CLN's setchannel command.
.PP
Output: JSON response from CLN's setchannel command.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-min-htlc-set (1)
